#: ../../introduction.rst:10 5d275717c1ca4563b7056ce2544b66f9
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdução"

#: ../../introduction.rst:13 b812b49edb544263a1edcab8ed983d3d
msgid "The problem and the solution"
